165
00:07:34,170 --> 00:07:36,270
Now for the funnest part,
the examples.

166
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,670
Keep these super simple.

167
00:07:37,670 --> 00:07:40,790
Save the complex, fancy examples
for a tutorial

168
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:42,510
another day.

169
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:44,140
Your example should demonstrate

170
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:45,490
this property only.

171
00:07:45,490 --> 00:07:48,140
Don't introduce other properties
or make the example

172
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:50,880
dependent upon the knowledge
of other properties.

173
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:55,210
Also, the example should
be self explanatory.

174
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:57,970
To create an example, start
with a new codelet at

175
00:07:57,970 --> 00:07:59,220
code.webplatform.org.

176
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:01,300

177
