name to the codelet.

179
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:09,940
Then I replace the dummy
content with my own.

180
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:15,200
You should test your example in
all of the major browsers.

181
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:17,000
